{"type": "article", "id": 21412, "title": "带宠物小屋的沙发", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-28T07:31:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 96, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133913zglW8UZOy1xTpKHj.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这张沙发带有一个木质的小隔间，它可以成为宠物的小屋——如果它能安心在里面待着。小隔间可以从左至右任意移动，上面是一个放茶水的桌面。没有动物住的时候，盒子里可以放上杂志，增添了一份灵动的生活气息。泰国的一家专做木家具的公司 deesawat 生产了这件家具，是用柚木做的，它也很适合放在户外。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150932Qjzxn3XDwhi7qlPS.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"759\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.92787286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150933J4roYb6SjRpdcP0I.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"544\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150934kRxXNZvhoYSi1rzd.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261509348UsF9GPbSvTg0Btm.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072615093597EWuOzcg0R4stBi.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.35452323\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150935iu9ceGl14r8P0VFH.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"302\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.36919315\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}